{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Midnight Evil</strong></h2><br>It's late at night and you've discovered a mysterious book that seems to have its own evil agenda. <br><br>As you begin to read through it, you realize that you are not alone.<br><br>The only way to free yourself from this fiendish nightmare is to finish reading. <br><br>In this story driven, voice activated, sit-and-survive horror game, don't forget to check your surroundings..<br><br>Also, be sure to make direct eye contact.<br><br>Can you survive the night?<br><br>Switch between <strong>Narrate Mode</strong> (speak into microphone - Windows 10 only) or <strong>Listen Mode</strong> (fully voice acted - all other Windows OS's) to make it through the chapters!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>A familiar Sit-And-Survive play style!<br></li><li>A full spooky narrative about ancient beings!<br></li><li>The ability to play with your microphone! (Currently Windows 10 only)<br></li><li>Fully voice acted if you don't have Windows 10 or a microphone!<br></li><li>Virtual Operating System / Game Console, Otori; with unlockable games and applications!<br></li><li>Steam Achievements!<br></li><li>Charming cheesy 80's horror environment and comedic relief!<br></li><li>Nick Gloom's self-absorbed ego.</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1030360/extras/molewhacker_2.gif?t=1722570546\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1030360/extras/scare.gif?t=1722570546\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Story Mode","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1030360/a237a8f7498248e21b9b20664fd85b28d002b3bd.jpg"},{"name":"Otori","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1030360/ac98d609a51acd2c17754984e054c44ee1dfbd50.jpg"},{"name":"Data_Block_23DE","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steams